<div id=3D"outline-container-3" class=3D"outline-2">
<h2 id=3D"3">Timere 0.1.3 - Dealing with time and time zones has never been=
 easier</h2>
<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-3">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-timere-0-1-3-dealing-wi=
th-time-and-time-zones-has-never-been-easier/7173/2">https://discuss.ocaml.=
org/t/ann-timere-0-1-3-dealing-with-time-and-time-zones-has-never-been-easi=
er/7173/2</a>
</p>
</div>

<div id=3D"outline-container-org2f960a0" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"org2f960a0">Darren announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-org2f960a0">
<p>
